{"tid":413483,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"✈️一個人嘅18日日本之旅 別有一番感受🇯🇵","createTime":"2017-09-25T12:55:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T16:55:14.000Z","uid":147203,"like":14,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a4b3e7138375ba3260464b899d393fd0d1933386","tid":413483,"uid":147203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T12:55:35.000Z","msg":"小弟係8月份沿東海道新幹線遊咗轉，分別係大阪 京都 名古屋 富士 東京 行咗都幾多地方。今次帶著一個背包就出發，體驗一下背包客嘅感覺。<br />\n<br />\n今次開po主要分享下周圍挽嘅心得。日本絕對係一個熱門嘅旅遊地方。唔知大家係住、玩、食、交通等有咩心得。<br />\n我會嘗試回憶返我之前嘅經歷，一part一part咁寫返篇完整嘅遊記出黎，其實我本來冇打算分享，所以冇影到太多相，有不足屌細力D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。但最后依趟旅行都帶黎唔錯嘅回憶，姑且就分享下啦。<br />\n<br />\n睇睇反應如何在更新<br />\n上幾張圖先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/25/205408_606e2dcce731b7d32d366eaa8f4115aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F25%2F205408_606e2dcce731b7d32d366eaa8f4115aa.jpg&h=85f04a9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/25/205409_364330732f0830a6194ba3188da4bafa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F25%2F205409_364330732f0830a6194ba3188da4bafa.jpg&h=990e95a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/25/205409_5465489f0c9eee145c903a121e734dee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F25%2F205409_5465489f0c9eee145c903a121e734dee.jpg&h=b16f5627&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e60dd96db719ed8cd9ac0a90642eff455cf4ec01","tid":413483,"uid":69939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:02:55.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"d73e8ab6de344abf2c3514ec4b4f5428ce1d66e2","tid":413483,"uid":67529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:04:05.000Z","msg":"留