64330732f0830a6194ba3188da4bafa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F25%2F205409_364330732f0830a6194ba3188da4bafa.jpg&h=990e95a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/25/205409_5465489f0c9eee145c903a121e734dee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F25%2F205409_5465489f0c9eee145c903a121e734dee.jpg&h=b16f5627&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔識日文 一個人去建唔建議⋯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都有d麻煩 不過整體都還好 。不過係名古屋同新宿試過俾馬夫搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09130da3535e94f25c36a710395fb1dda8fe3aec","tid":413483,"uid":147203,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:54:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小弟係8月份沿東海道新幹線遊咗轉，分別係大阪 京都 名古屋 富士 東京 行咗都幾多地方。今次帶著一個背包就出發，體驗一下背包客嘅感覺。<br />\n<br />\n今次開po主要分享下周圍挽嘅心得。日本絕對係一個熱門嘅旅遊地方。唔知大家係住、玩、食、交通等有咩心得。<br />\n我會嘗試回憶返我之前嘅經歷，一part一part咁寫返篇完整嘅遊記出黎，其實我本來冇打算分享，所以冇影到太多相，有不足屌細力D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。但最后依趟旅行都帶黎唔錯嘅回憶，姑且就分享下啦。<br />\n<br />\n睇睇反應如何在更新<br />\n上幾張圖先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/25/205408_606e2dcce731b7d32d366eaa8f4115aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F25%2F205408_606e2dcce731b7d32d366eaa8f4115aa.jpg&h=85f04a9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/25/205409_364330732f0830a6194ba3188da4bafa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F25%2F205409_364330732f0830a6194ba3188da4bafa.jpg&h=990e95a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/25/205409_5465489f0c9eee145c903a121e734dee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F25%2F205409_5465489f0c9eee145c903a121e734dee.jpg&h=b16f5627&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔識日文 一個人去建唔建議⋯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都有d麻煩 不過整體都還好 。就係名古屋同新宿試過俾馬夫搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0d5d1d0e64059335a58687737a56a290de045773","tid":413483,"uid":147203,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T10:05:10.000Z","msg":"講下今個行程先啦<br />\n依個行程大概約算3萬，不過不失，起碼唔使去到窮遊嘅地步。<br />\n<br />\n準備行程<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/26/175513_ac02249e8433dc43dca0e12ef9698de2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F26%2F175513_ac02249e8433dc43dca0e12ef9698de2.jpg&h=2e33749d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n帶咗兩本旅遊書，一部notebook，四日要換嘅衫，就一個背囊出發。因為周圍去嘅關係，所以就臨走個幾日先係東京買喼算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 瀟灑嘅旅行，想去邊就去邊<br />\n<br />\n8月都算係旺季，想買平價廉航嘅係依d月份出發多d留意機票價格變動<br />\n今次我去程回程機票分開買<br />\n去程：樂桃MM064 $583 HKG-OSK<br />\n回程：jestar $856            TYO-HKG<br />\n<br />\n樂桃整理感覺良好，廉航座位係窄都係咁，空姐真係jeng，起碼我坐架機d空姐都有一定質素。唔記得影空姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/26/175754_fbb535b3dd3999076946624a08d287f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F26%2F175754_fbb535b3dd3999076946624a08d287f6.jpg&h=0ee28665&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/26/175755_5b8657648d7d3756b5e18fb244d0a430.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F26%2F175755_5b8657648d7d3756b5e18fb244d0a430.jpg&h=24d3b9fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南海電鐵特急，係樂桃買慳300羊，價錢幾乎同快速普通差唔多。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/26/175856_702d94266ce5ab6eef050571d6540503.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F26%2F175856_702d94266ce5ab6eef050571d6540503.jpg&h=dca1fe23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/26/180201_8086afdad0bc162661c1fd3b5a85eb0f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F26%2F180201_8086afdad0bc162661c1fd3b5a85eb0f.jpg&h=22f5dd83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入面座位都幾大，加小小錢坐得舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/26/180202_e09840ce6b1b7006aeae4b821adf1d38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F26%2F180202_e09840ce6b1b7006aeae4b821adf1d38.jpg&h=e8db1c4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實係出發前一晚guesthouse房主同我講我book果間大廳果度d床位裝修緊，同我講要同個房客係一間房嘅雙人床訓一晚，跟住之後嘅兩晚你自己住。我真係心唸要變基佬。雖然佢話取消都冇問題，不過算啦，依家改都麻煩。<br />\n<br />\n波蘭嘅backpacker，佢用jr張青春18要來回東京我真係佩服佢，單程9粒鐘真係爛屎忽。<br />\nCut走我自己先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/26/180021_1353bc8de69bc586c070d385410b3c41.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F26%2F180021_1353bc8de69bc586c070d385410b3c41.jpg&h=9049ab37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/26/180046_2f6aad6aca27d9156e2013e75913352a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F26%2F180046_2f6aad6aca27d9156e2013e75913352a.jpg&h=53bd82e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一晚到難波都11點，求其食d嘢就返返住處<br />\n<br />\n我真係好鍾意自動販賣機個濃縮巴士，好撚過癮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/26/180121_49782b547a771015ac55389822f5d82e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F26%2F180121_49782b547a771015ac55389822f5d82e.jpg&h=e790c4a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n返返住處，櫻川，距離難波一個站，超近，隨意衝行程返去補給。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/26/180336_b1e9e32f362bd1adbb38e6af425bd07f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F26%2F180336_b1e9e32f362bd1adbb38e6af425bd07f.jpg&h=a0cb2120&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/26/180338_7caea16eb950cc603d6b20bff7163b60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F26%2F180338_7caea16eb950cc603d6b20bff7163b60.jpg&h=e49fd245&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一part係咁咁，下集再見<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"285971a3b13d0bb0c98eb0d48121b8fb6992ef3d","tid":413483,"uid":56311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T13:42:09.000Z","msg":"留名,有冇去叫雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"335d66170413519eafce2ae6c663957f2027ae47","tid":413483,"uid":102475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T22:25:09.000Z","msg":"繼續繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8de4a1f79aa70c9e9f8f087a328586454392b67","tid":413483,"uid":56311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T00:36:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/c/c9/樓主，我們到了，你在哪裡？.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20090923152016\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fc%2Fc9%2F%E6%A8%93%E4%B8%BB%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E5%88%B0%E4%BA%86%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%A0%E5%9C%A8%E5%93%AA%E8%A3%A1%EF%BC%9F.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20090923152016&h=494de2a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"179a49386c5e25362c961af09d0b7e2c7a6cf341","tid":413483,"uid":37942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T01:09:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61dee5f896fefa4a6c2095764b0af55d9e14b302","tid":413483,"uid":42601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T01:11:46.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"1048de5946a98dcc985a7d694df5bc562451596a","tid":413483,"uid":42344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T01:33:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"407aee3ef295391f871f271f32f52abb50ee14f2","tid":413483,"uid":44833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T01:41:03.000Z","msg":"快撚啲出文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1685419465003e10ab2dfc5a49d889ac91a5f922","tid":413483,"uid":67529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T09:44:41.000Z","msg":"爛左尾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9734f9fe5a000a9a5404dab08c5780d2e0106d2c","tid":413483,"uid":106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T09:48:07.000Z","msg":"有冇互含<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a03bd76eb1141d3bfcc9e28da16da085225158c4","tid":413483,"uid":147203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T12:18:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>爛左尾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n馬上更新"},{"pid":"8b2ed2e5eea04468010497c364a98659d4014ec0","tid":413483,"uid":147203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T12:21:47.000Z","msg":"然而，尋晚成晚訓唔到，自己一張床訓開唔習慣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 朝早6點幾就出去食左個早餐。成個人冇乜精神，但冇理由浪費一日訓覺。同波蘭佬道別後於是出發。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/202140_c98af2fb2a57098fccc3e2ae77b6cab6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F202140_c98af2fb2a57098fccc3e2ae77b6cab6.jpg&h=86b45836&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用我早早預定嘅大阪周遊卡去衝行程，依張嘢CP值極高，除左地鐵免費搭，有30個以上嘅景點都係隨便挽。3300羊兩日，絕對抵回票價！我依兩日計過都係佢身上用咗10000羊以上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/202103_4067d2d4fa6f260642988b508a15e282.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F202103_4067d2d4fa6f260642988b508a15e282.jpg&h=828e247a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一站鳩衝去天王寺動物園。周遊卡包辦我嘅行程，但依幾日大阪天氣真係好撚熱，成36度，邊行底褲都真係會跟住出汗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住去坐hepfive，自己一個去做摩天輪真係好撚尷尬。望著其他人一對情侶或者一班人，我自己就一個人包咗成個摩天輪，有d周身唔自在。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己出得黎挽，預咗厚面皮。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n摩天輪上面可以自己插手機播歌，我開到好撚大聲。上面往落去嘅鐵路景色真係好jeng，搵到動漫果種feel。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住去咗梅田嘅空中展望台，今日依度好似係煙花大會，6點前會叫你離開依度。其實我真係好攰。好眼訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住既然飛田新地距離我個住處算緊，等我折返去就算唔幫襯考察下都好。真係冇相，果度係唔俾影依個你地應該都知。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n飛田新地我過黎嘅時候覺得治安冇d人話咁差，可能未到晚黑我唔知。有聽聞話d人叫完雞後會俾支棒棒糖你，其他嘅龜婆見到就唔會再煩，又真係俾我見到成班好似係高中生手上各一支，真係好似特登話俾你知我叫完雞啦咁。真係幾好笑。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日冇乜精神真係7點幾就返返去沖涼訓覺<br />\n<br />\n原諒我繼續寫落去下集<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4037d77da43ff4fb0c21cd8629e138db01b4a2b3","tid":413483,"uid":147203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T12:24:37.000Z","msg":"補番d相先 唔小心send咗上去<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/202318_ab8c597f68b467055e5bd4256ad1da14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F202318_ab8c597f68b467055e5bd4256ad1da14.jpg&h=5c20efed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/202319_b2049ee0fcb6d1bec3e59a6187ae3776.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F202319_b2049ee0fcb6d1bec3e59a6187ae3776.jpg&h=28229744&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/202319_9f37acbe1ee6f8f82d16b0ee21308974.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F202319_9f37acbe1ee6f8f82d16b0ee21308974.jpg&h=df675f35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/202320_2d167df7c070d164c02c4b928091e389.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F202320_2d167df7c070d164c02c4b928091e389.jpg&h=0fbf7f8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/202423_2784856d9b27767c57a80822c749af5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F202423_2784856d9b27767c57a80822c749af5b.jpg&h=1d92a53e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/202424_1f8728125a5e9e86adbfbdf31c0f5284.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F202424_1f8728125a5e9e86adbfbdf31c0f5284.jpg&h=d404e361&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/202424_e696d7a2a7a2479b0c46c434eafd29a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F202424_e696d7a2a7a2479b0c46c434eafd29a2.jpg&h=7e163a8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/202425_e696d7a2a7a2479b0c46c434eafd29a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F202425_e696d7a2a7a2479b0c46c434eafd29a2.jpg&h=9601aa2a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f371945b5d9dfed0281e62e4909f6731cf5be94b","tid":413483,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T12:32:28.000Z","msg":"推"}]}